	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Music from 1001 Spikes</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><a href="http://rushjet1.bandcamp.com/album/music-from-1001-spikes" class="postlink"><img src="http://f0.bcbits.com/img/a4028267657_2.jpg" alt="Image" /></a><br /><br />I released my first commercial game album, Music from 1001 Spikes a couple weeks ago.<br /><br />I'm not going to release it in NSF format as way too many .ftm files were used for that to be even remotely possible, plus several songs use different expansions (FDS, VRC6, MMC5, 2a03-only).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
